  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Forest_GM_Finale
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - So the Guardian judged you worthy. I never doubted it. You are a Novice no longer, but an Apprentice.
  - That Fragment is real power, not a trinket. Refined elements are within your reach now, and recipes that once died in your hands will bear fruit.
  - Explore, experiment, and when your hands are sure, descend to the Underground. We are only beginning, you and I.
